videos.description: UCLA's Lonzo Ball gets a block on Washington's Markelle Fultz and he gets a lay-up in transition.
videos.headline: Lonzo Ball blocks Markelle Fultz and scores on the other end

videos.description: UCLA's Aaron Holiday lobs an alley-oop pass to Lonzo Ball who finishes with a 2-handed jam.
videos.headline: Lonzo Ball throws down an alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Washington's Markelle Fultz uses a great spin move to get around UCLA's Thomas Welsh on his way to the basket for a lay-up.
videos.headline: Fultz's spin move gives him an open lay-up
